description: The power and brains behind Pixel 8a: Google Tensor G3 is Pixel’s most powerful chip yet. It makes Pixel 8a fast and efficient. And Google AI gives you personalized help throughout the day. Amazing photos and videos, every time: With fully upgraded sensors and advanced image processing, the Pixel Camera reveals vivid colors and striking details in any light. A stunning display: The 6.1-inch high-resolution display delivers sharp, vivid colors and detail. And it has a refresh rate of up to 120Hz for smoother scrolling. Circle to Search: A super easy way to search: Circle to search anything right from the app you’re in. Just draw a circle with your finger around an image, text, or video, and Google AI finds it fast. The super dependable, all-day battery: Pixel’s Adaptive Battery can last over 24 hours. Turn on Extreme Battery Saver, and it can last up to 72 hours. And it charges faster than ever. Powered by Android. And it's easy to switch to Pixel: Transfer your contacts, photos, messages, and more. And Pixel already comes with your favorite Google apps. Tiny details. Epic photos: With Macro Focus, the smallest subjects can become spectacular images. Group pics, perfected: Did someone blink or look away? Pixel’s Best Take combines similar photos into one fantastic picture where everyone looks their best. Video sounds even better, just like that: Audio Magic Eraser uses Google AI to reduce disruptive noises like cars and wind and highlight the sounds you want. Security you can depend on: With Google Tensor G3 and the Titan M2 security chip, Pixel is built with layers of security to help keep your personal info safe.
